FBIS3-15385 "drsov044_g_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Nation To Pay Part of Debt for Gas LD0403193294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1600 GMT 4 Mar 94 LD0403193294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Belarus Government today found 31 billion rubles to service its debt to Russia for its gas and oil, which, as is known, exceeds 400 billion rubles. The Republican Government is prepared to apply compulsory measures to those Belarus companies that owe Russia, said Mikhail Myasnikov, the first deputy chairman of the Council of Ministers. In the deputy prime minister's words, the Belarus Government will do everything possible to clear the major part of its debt to Russia in the near future.
